    33→\\n    34→The script writes:\\n    35→\\n    36→- `/tmp/kiro-auth-bundle.tar.gz`\\n    37→- `/tmp/kiro-auth-bundle.tar.gz.b64`\\n    38→\\n    39→## Upload secret\\n    40→\\n    41→```bash\\n    42→gh secret set KIRO_AUTH_BUNDLE_B64 < /tmp/kiro-auth-bundle.tar.gz.b64\\n    43→```\\n    44→\\n    45→## Rotation\\n    46→\\n    47→Rotate the secret whenever:\\n    48→\\n    49→- Kiro token expires or is revoked\\n    50→- CI `kiro-cli whoami` returns `account: null`\\n    51→- Bot account credentials are changed\\n    52→\"}]},\"uuid\":\"7e002a46-200b-4715-8454-5811748290bd\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-03T19:07:59.373Z\"},\"normalizedMessages\":[],\"type\":\"agent_progress\",\"prompt\":\"\",\"agentId\":\"a0f69859fc1a7e8ed\"},\"toolUseID\":\"agent_msg_01RZLEMWM4zTLa9f6GfFcU1k\",\"parentToolUseID\":\"toolu_01EZQovuCTvbmbYQviSz5UyX\",\"uuid\":\"9c7bec99-ee52-4261-baa5-517bef918a2a\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-03T19:07:59.375Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"9c7bec99-ee52-4261-baa5-517bef918a2a\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alisha/Projects/wt/kiro-oneshot\",\"sessionId\":\"8a949619-8aae-4f1a-a46c-6bbf236c34b3\",\"version\":\"2.1.63\",\"gitBranch\":\"alisha/kiro-oneshot\",\"slug\":\"glittery-waddling-parrot\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"message\":{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-03T19:07:59.807Z\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_018rM1aJfYDfMd8sXhi3fcFJ\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01DCXudx4irBcNWpiLSmm3ho\",\"name\":\"Read\",\"input\":{\"file_path\":\"/Users/alisha/Projects/wt/kiro-oneshot/cmd/entire/cli/setup.go\"},\"caller\":{\"type\":\"direct\"}}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":4892,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":110222,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":4892},\"output_tokens\":24,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",